 Marsh and other seedless grapefruit, excluding pink grapefruit, are
renamed as Marsh and other seedless grapefruit, excluding red
grapefruit;

 Duncan and other seeded grapefruit, excluding pink grapefruit, are
renamed as Duncan and other seeded grapefruit, excluding red
grapefruit;

 The shipment does not exceed a total of 15 standard packed cartons
(12 bushels) of fruit, either a single fruit or a combination of two
or more fruits;

 The fruit is used for animal feed and is not offered for resale,
disposed of, or in any way handled so as to enter fresh fruit
channels;

The quantity does not exceed 1,000
